{"tid":399081,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟呢種係咩心態？求解答....","createTime":"2017-09-13T16:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T18:04:26.000Z","uid":118354,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"585908978b45b0c3b7da890f96899a1cc21d6747","tid":399081,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:01:57.000Z","msg":"我同我前任男友之前一齊左五年<br />\n分手之後就識左現任男友 而家一齊左三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係唔知點解 佢成日都會提起我前任既名<br />\n而且成日都會問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n: x 係咪咁樣對你架 <br />\n:你係咪成日咁樣對住 x<br />\n<br />\n當我講錯野個陣 佢就會話 <br />\n:唔怪之得x唔鍾意你唔同你一齊啦<br />\n<br />\n當我問返佢係咪妒忌既時候(因為佢成日都咁講搞到我覺得佢係妒忌我同前任一齊左好多年 以為我仲鍾意緊我前任)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢就話 唔係呀 <br />\n<br />\n我真係好想知點解佢成日都會咁樣講嘢 <br />\n猜唔透呀大佬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818f67fd76a72b51d93c36c9539de6c154bd1a6a","tid":399081,"uid":65390,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:04:19.000Z","msg":"自卑到要不斷同你ex比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正廢柴"},{"pid":"a1f51ac8e61ab373a00f222badba2ed487754dbd","tid":399081,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自卑到要不斷同你ex比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正廢柴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但其實外形同性格方面 真係現任好好多 <br />\n但我就係唔明 點解佢而家都會仲提起我前任個名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搞到我對呢個名揮之不去<br />\n好煩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b049edff4768e498e10e44f19a61f416c8cc07","tid":399081,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"認為自己同你ex唔同，唔想你用對ex既態度/方法對佢，不過佢咁樣講得証明曾經有人講過你壞話比佢知，係咪樓主自己都有前科<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f9cff8e4ad272e90b6ff3201c9c727e13aa174","tid":399081,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認為自己同你ex唔同，唔想你用對ex既態度/方法對佢，不過佢咁樣講得証明曾經有人講過你壞話比佢知，係咪樓主自己都有前科<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發誓冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋大家完全冇共同朋友 <br />\n但係佢哋大家住嘅區域都係一樣 隔住左條大馬路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但我相信佢哋一定冇見過面冇講過嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566d8b1a7b17c039abfc5f8f1435342e566b1275","tid":399081,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"當佢問完我 ：x 係咪咁樣對你<br />\n1:我答唔係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢就會話唔信囉 你一定都有咁樣對佢<br />\n2:我唔答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開頭我就話過咗去就算啦 都同佢分開咗 <br />\n但佢就會一直追問 究竟有冇姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗚嗚  究竟佢想我點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205a89cdfc4ae5a610530188a56b52150995ece7","tid":399081,"uid":131457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:32:46.000Z","msg":"係咪冇安全感怕你之前鐘意前任多過你宜家鐘意現任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78498ce7a68ae0f9fa36c04a6a730710d31a6f3","tid":399081,"uid":137556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"絲打，我都苦惱緊呢個問題<br />\n現任好鍾意同前度比較，小小事會化到好大，扯到同我前度有關<br />\n真心每次聽到好煩"},{"pid":"78f2d8f51d08dea39a0d11ddb4a81a7c9d73da4a","tid":399081,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪冇安全感怕你之前鐘意前任多過你宜家鐘意現任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開頭同現任一齊個時我係屬於比較被動 佢比較主動 但耐左 就變返係我主動 佢就被動 <br />\n好多時候 都係我主動講一啲甜言蜜語 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢淨係會比少少反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又或者會跟返我講嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係我想講 係佢冇乜俾到我安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f6b4b744770438838800255afc5348165b7ab3","tid":399081,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1ff043a660f6f6cfc811d5665dd993e2711fec7","tid":399081,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打，我都苦惱緊呢個問題<br />\n現任好鍾意同前度比較，小小事會化到好大，扯到同我前度有關<br />\n真心每次聽到好煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗚嗚 真係困擾左我好多年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd16271c9b8fd64c9ea16df295208985b9c0b8a2","tid":399081,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇字已經知你個處比左前度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022f6fc8635b9736a8500f9f13a151c01f8b45aa","tid":399081,"uid":65390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自卑到要不斷同你ex比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正廢柴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但其實外形同性格方面 真係現任好好多 <br />\n但我就係唔明 點解佢而家都會仲提起我前任個名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搞到我對呢個名揮之不去<br />\n好煩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲人表面正正常常<br />\n其實就收收埋埋<br />\n一路都介意你同ex拍左咁耐怕自己取代唔到佢<br />\n始終男人可能都會對女朋友俾ex掂過耿耿於懷<br />\n所以某程度上搵老婆要搵處女可能先係正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf767c78a54a4fe16cb99401f9cdc8d6d0fe28c","tid":399081,"uid":141663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:45:56.000Z","msg":"我現任都會咁。。"},{"pid":"02a53c2c15808aaddf38e5e07f39ba6cee1cc986","tid":399081,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇字已經知你個處比左前度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴表示係介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己諗諗"},{"pid":"3204de4401dd541d7acf6021ae8fce5f241bfa37","tid":399081,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:47:16.000Z","msg":"報返個年齡先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我22<br />\n佢28"},{"pid":"ffc6a988c0822f8226edca2c4b32a1b1c9862f49","tid":399081,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:48:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48db4c69df066d42a62dde71ba4238f1b5c5da67","tid":399081,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自卑到要不斷同你ex比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正廢柴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但其實外形同性格方面 真係現任好好多 <br />\n但我就係唔明 點解佢而家都會仲提起我前任個名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搞到我對呢個名揮之不去<br />\n好煩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲人表面正正常常<br />\n其實就收收埋埋<br />\n一路都介意你同ex拍左咁耐怕自己取代唔到佢<br />\n始終男人可能都會對女朋友俾ex掂過耿耿於懷<br />\n所以某程度上搵老婆要搵處女可能先係正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  香港依家應該冇咩可能搵到 <br />\n不過我其實都知道佢真係介意我同前任一齊左好耐 可能佢真係怕我會忘記唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但佢每次都提起個名叫我點忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0718e79cccd375f9d773d1472964fcdd92628fe6","tid":399081,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇字已經知你個處比左前度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍左5年冇扑過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n緊係有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  話冇你都唔信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過個處就唔係俾佢囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6defc23a1943900df0a6ffdbfb1b156afb81c0a","tid":399081,"uid":118354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我現任都會咁。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來有咁多人有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我已經成日都表達我好愛我男朋友 <br />\n唔單止說話行動我都做齊晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e96d945f23d836c4cd4bdee178a12902457aeca","tid":399081,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:56:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc476a0f7b6dcb767011009516ed935cf0579c6b","tid":399081,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇字已經知你個處比左前度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍左5年冇扑過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n緊係有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  話冇你都唔信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過個處就唔係俾佢囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實,雙方都有錯,你唔同佢講你的感受,你錯;佢對你發火,不理解你,佢錯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1eec9b1f2184e831d0a81695e54cbde4ac014d","tid":399081,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇字已經知你個處比左前度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍左5年冇扑過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n緊係有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  話冇你都唔信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過個處就唔係俾佢囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n挑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁咪即係比左前度囉 <br />\n之後仲要比呢個抽插左5年 <br />\n有冇人搵返個條公式出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1-1=0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你今後嘅幸福係無限接近無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a5467e507bb38bee9a94318f07ddca7bdcd7aa","tid":399081,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"妳試下發一次對佢脾氣睇下會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b47a238267c435f44e048a5edc6ca229fd021da","tid":399081,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>妳試下發一次對佢脾氣睇下會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n妳試下對佢發一次脾氣睇下會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}